			<strong>Electric Revolution:</strong>
			<p>Electric vehicles (EVs) continue to gain momentum, with major automakers investing heavily in eco-friendly mobility solutions. The rise of electric cars is not just a trend; it's a paradigm shift towards a more sustainable future.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
