			<p>The dream of self-driving cars is becoming a reality. Advanced driver-assistance systems (ADAS) and artificial intelligence are paving the way for safer and more efficient transportation. The concept of hands-free driving is no longer confined to science fiction.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>Hypercar Marvels:</strong>
			<p>Hypercars are pushing the boundaries of speed and performance. Cutting-edge engineering and aerodynamics are giving birth to machines that redefine what's possible on the road. These cars are not just a mode of transportation; they're a statement of engineering prowess.</p>
		</li>
		<li>
			<strong>Sustainable Materials:</strong>
			<p>Automakers are embracing sustainable practices by incorporating eco-friendly materials in car manufacturing. From recycled plastics to plant-based components, the industry is moving towards a greener approach, reducing the environmental impact of vehicle production.</p>
		</li>
	</ol>

</article>

